{
  "stem": "13219.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I spoke to them in 1968, and they said they know that he was alive with them, and he couldn't stand being alone while his family was killed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He dug himself-- they made him dig a grave, and they shot him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was about 52 or 54 years old I think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, some of them went to the Russian underground-- Russian-- went underground in the woods.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them joined the Russian partisans, and I met a few guys, which they were with him in the Russian partisans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember the name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A beautiful face, a nice zaftig woman, and very good natured woman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think that if they find out that one of them harbored Jews, they killed them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just told you, Mokwin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it's about six or seven miles from Berezne.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, she was in Mokwin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't far from river.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She lived almost-- not far from the river.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She let us stay there for about four days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then she came down one night and she said, people are talking that I am hiding Jews. ' I would say you should go away.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she gave us some food and a jacket or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then when we went out there was a big church with the-- with the-- was standing on pillars.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, the church was-- there was no cellar, but it was open.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went in there-- figured to hide there for a while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we met up with a Russian soldier, a deserter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he thought that we have gold or money, because he knew that we were Jewish, and I think he wanted to take us both.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
